snippet.title: Yankee's Journey and Fine Coffee.
snippet.description:
DIY, Outdoors,  High Adventure and Fine Coffee Drinking.  1st channel on YouTube to start out with PREPPER in his name back in 2009,  before PREPPING became a joke. I have always been the type to prepare and was doing that before there was a "YouTube"

WARNING!!!   If you don't like Jesus... you are really going to HATE me.  Jesus loves you, but I may not want to be around you.
